  <data name="label1.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>TwistBot scans the gem grid and finds a move to make. Moves that are the next in the bonus (shown on bottom left) are the top priority. The next is matches larger than 3 gems. Finally, there's standard 3 gem matches.</value>
  </data>
